# S1-G0 · I5 — Code owners.
#
# Fiscal is compliance-critical: the platform is never the fiscal issuer
# (ADR-0006), and fiscal changes carry legal risk. Any PR touching packs/fiscal/
# requires review from the designated fiscal reviewers. Enforced by branch
# protection ("Require review from Code Owners") on the pushed repo.
#
# NOTE: the handles below are placeholders — replace with the real GitHub
# teams/users before enabling Code Owner review, or GitHub will report an
# unknown-owner error.

# Default owner for everything.
*                       @t8mhq/core-maintainers

# Fiscal pack — designated reviewers.
/packs/fiscal/          @t8mhq/fiscal-reviewers

# Fiscal compliance issue template travels with the fiscal owners too.
/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/fiscal-compliance.yml  @t8mhq/fiscal-reviewers
